CRITICAL VARIATION RULES:
- The 3 variants MUST have **different background color themes** (e.g., dark / cream / white)
- Do NOT copy PRD color tokens identically across variants
- Interpret PRD primary color differently per variant (gradient glow vs pastel+accent vs sparse accent)
